    "defense": {
      "critical_failure": "The target is afflicted with stage 2 divine plague.   \n  \n**Divine Plague** (disease) **Level 1**; Stage 1 clumsy 1, enfeebled 1, or stupefied 1 (1 round); **Stage 2** slowed 1 and clumsy 1, enfeebled 1, or stupefied 1 (1 round); **Stage 3** clumsy 1, enfeebled 1, or stupefied 1 and the target can\u2019t recover from the condition until they are cured (1 day)",
